PART B — FALSIFICATION OF EVENT 20 (CONNECTOME HARMONICS)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

The shipped proof_of_property() is a TAUTOLOGY by trajectory construction:
  • RLHF traj = [1,2,3,1,2,3,...] + [8,9,8,9,...]
    → uses only 5 of 15 vocab slots, partitioned into TWO disjoint cycles
    → mathematically guaranteed to have ≥ 11 disconnected components
    → eigenvalues[1] is forced to 0 by the spectral theorem
  • BIO traj  = permutation visiting ALL 15 slots in a single path
    → mathematically guaranteed to be connected
    → eigenvalues[1] is the algebraic connectivity of a 14-edge path graph
  Result: assertion `bio_fiedler > rlhf_fiedler` reduces to
          "0.0251 > 0.0", i.e. "connected > disconnected", which is true
          BY HOW THE INPUTS WERE CONSTRUCTED, not by anything Laplacian.

Falsification battery (`/tmp/connectome_falsify.py`):

  TEST 1 — Shipped trajectories                      assertion holds (rigged).
  TEST 2 — Relabel attack: swap which is called      assertion FLIPS.
           "bio" vs "rlhf"
           → proves the metric is testing trajectory SHAPE, not biology.
  TEST 3 — 5 random trials, equal lengths, but        assertion holds 5/5
           preserving "RLHF=split-halves, BIO=perm"   (still rigged at the
                                                       construction level).
  TEST 4 — Length asymmetry: short BIO vs long RLHF  result still flips depending
           (real LLM trajectories have unequal       on which one is longer.
            sample counts) → measurement breaks.
  TEST 5 — REALISTIC RLHF: preferential-attachment   produces a CONNECTED
           "stuck-in-a-corner" loop (the actual      graph (1 component).
           failure mode of safety-tuned LLMs)        AG31's metric calls this
                                                     "biological". WRONG.
  TEST 6 — REALISTIC BIO: dispersed exploration       produces a DISCONNECTED
           with isolated novel tokens (RAF           graph. AG31's metric calls
           nucleation, the actual signature of       this "RLHF". WRONG.
           creative cognition)

CONCLUSION: in the realistic regime — which is what the architect actually
asked about — the metric is not just weak, it is ANTICORRELATED with the
property it claims to measure. RLHF preferential attachment looks
"biological", and biological novelty looks "RLHF".

